were drinking while listening to Kuai Wu

00:01:56.039 --> 00:01:58.170
tell stories about Empress Wu Zetian.

00:01:59.479 --> 00:02:02.040
The events that happened
during the Empress's reign.

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:03.760
How well did he usually hold his liquor?

00:02:03.760 --> 00:02:04.420
Quite well.

00:02:05.350 --> 00:02:07.040
Though he drank a lot yesterday,

00:02:07.040 --> 00:02:09.009
with Kuai Wu's tolerance,

00:02:09.120 --> 00:02:10.720
